snippet.title: Amber Heard's Lawyer QUITS the CASE | Flixet
snippet.description:
It’s been revealed that Heard’s top lawyer, Roberta Kaplan and her team have quit the lawsuit against her ex-husband, Johnny Depp. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

The legal back and forth between Aquaman star Amber Heard and her ex-husband, Fantastic Beasts star Johnny Depp, has taken another strange turn with Amber Heard's defense lawyers splitting with the actress ahead of her upcoming libel trial.

It’s been revealed that Heard’s top lawyer, Roberta Kaplan and her team have quit the lawsuit against her ex-husband, Johnny Depp.
